		"job_name": "Inspect an old battlefield",
        "job_description": "You find an odd offer among the usual stream of scams, laughably underpaid jobs, and other disguised pyramid schemes. This is less an ad and more of an archive about old events in a remote location.\nMost of the documents are part of a leaked dossier from a ==Luddic Church military internal investigation==. They relate to a disastrous clearing operation that saw two large fleets destroyed in a ==Remnant stronghold==. However, redacted parts suggest there might be something more at play.\nObviously the leak gave rise to all kinds of conspiracy theories and wild speculations. From incompetence to back-stabbing, to a false-flag operation, to mythical space monsters; every hypothesis got its time in the spotlight. In the end,  there is only so much tangible information to gather from the leaked documents.\nSomeone ostensibly compiled this dossier thinking it might be titillating enough for a commander to take their fleet and find out what is lurking there. If the losses reported are accurate, there is at minimum a significant amount of salvage to reclaim.",
