		"job_name": "The Red Hand resurfaces",
		"job_description": "[EXCERPTS FROM A MILITARY JOURNAL ARTICLE]\nThe famous pirate ship ==\"Red Hand\"== has been spotted recently within an assembling pirate force in the $constellation region.\n[...]\nRumors suggest that she now has a new captain after her failed bombardment attempt of a Hegemony stronghold a few cycles ago. The damaged ship managed to escape retribution then, and once again vanished to her hiding hole in the fringes.\n[...]\nDetails are sparse but the Lion's Intelligence Services are positing that ==Sindria could be targeted== by that rising Pirate captain. Given the dedication and competence one must possess to get the coveted the top rank of the nicknamed \"Avatar of Vengeance\" crew, they are taking this threat very seriously. Mobilizing the Lion's Guard against a mere pirate however could be interpreted as a sign of weakness, thus a reward of ==$reward credits== has been offered to select renowned mercenary outfits for the definitive neutralization of the \"Red Hand\".",
