		"job_description": "You notice another posting suspiciously similar to the one from ==the Church official== you got a while ago:\n\"Our recent improvements in cross-referencing pattern methods revealed some ==suspicious Remnant activity in the fringes==, and we suspect the blight of AI is once again on the move. My Duty to my Lord Ludd compels me and my organization to hire a team to investigate and expunge this cursed nest.\"\nYour Intelligence officer quickly gets back to you with an indication that the likely author of the previous job offer was expelled from the Church's ministry for using improper computerized tools and mishandling funds. They seem to be actively hunted for running away after further misappropriating large sums of money. While this job looks legit, there seems to be more at play in the background.",
